column2: SELECT o.objid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 objID, type, ra, dec, psfMag_u, psfMag_g, psfMag_r, psfMag_i, psfMag_z, dered_u, dered_g, dered_r, dered_i, dered_z, extinction_u, extinction_g, extinction_r, extinction_i, extinction_z, mode = #, type = # into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.MyRaDecPairs AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
